VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT cidr_blocks\s*=\s*\["0\.0\.0\.0/0"\]|cidr_ipv6\s*=\s*\["::/0"\]
WHEN EXPR MISSING:from_port\s*=\s*(?:443|80)\b
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects security group rules or firewall rules allowing ingress from all IP addresses.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Security Group Open to All Traffic (0.0.0.0/0).
